        <h3 itemprop="name">❓ Veniti la Promenada Mall pentru petreceri?</h3>
        <div itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
          <p itemprop="text">Avem experienta cu petrecerile in zona Promenada Mall. Lucram cu sali private din incinta sau in restaurantele din mall.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
