      <div class="faq-item" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
        <h3 itemprop="name">❓ Cat costa un animator pentru o villa party in Pipera?</h3>
        <div itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
          <p itemprop="text">Pachetele raman aceleasi: 490 / 840 / 1290 RON. Indiferent de locatie (vila, apartament sau sala), pretul pachetului nu se schimba.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
        <h3 itemprop="name">❓ Aveti experienta cu petreceri tematice sofisticate in Aviatorilor?</h3>
        <div itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
          <p itemprop="text">Da — facem petreceri tematice complete: decor, personaj coordonat, jocuri tematice. Contactati-ne pentru pachete custom.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
        <h3 itemprop="name">❓ Exista taxa de deplasare din Aviatorilor pana la Voluntari sau Pipera (Ilfov)?</h3>
        <div itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
          <p itemprop="text">Nu — acoperim toata zona Aviatorilor, Pipera si Voluntari fara taxa suplimentara de transport.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-box">
      <h2>Rezerva animator în <span style="color:var(--primary)">Aviației</span></h2>
      <p>⚡ Disponibilitate limitata in weekend — locurile se ocupa rapid!<br>Garantie contractuala: daca copiii nu s-au simtit bine, nu platesti!</p>
      <div class="btns" style="justify-content:center">
        <a href="tel:+40722744377" class="btn-p cta">📞 0722 744 377</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/40722744377" class="btn-wa cta">💬 WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="/petreceri/sector-1">← Sectorul 1</a>
